headline.main: A Relative of Couscous Finds a Wider Fan Base
headline.print_headline: A Relative of Couscous Finds a Wider Fan Base

lead_paragraph: Mexico is prepared to negotiate changes to the North American Free Trade Agreement to modernize the 23-year-old open trade pact grouping the United States, Canada and Mexico, Economy Minister Ildefonso Guajardo said on Friday.
